    "minides": "World's first Formula E-themed electric SUV — motorsport DNA meets everyday electric performance, launched in collaboration with Mahindra Racing.",
    "description": "The Mahindra BE 6 Formula E Edition is a special-edition variant of the BE 6 electric coupe SUV, launched on 27 November 2025 at ₹23.69 lakh. It is offered in two variants — FE2 and FE3 — both powered by the 79 kWh battery with a rear-axle-mounted electric motor producing 282 bhp and 380 Nm, capable of 0–100 km/h in 6.7 seconds and a top speed of 202 km/h. The Formula E Edition is distinguished by Firestorm Orange accents lifted from Mahindra's Formula E race car, updated front bumper with round projector headlamps and gloss-black bezels, orange brake calipers, white tow hooks, roof-mounted spoiler, sporty sill panelling, and a Formula E-themed startup animation. The FE2 adds 360-degree camera, front parking sensors, and auto-folding ORVMs over the comparable Pack Two variant. The FE3 further adds intelligent adaptive suspension and 20-inch alloy wheels. Both variants carry the 79 kWh battery (vs 59 kWh in Pack Three Select) and are built on Mahindra's INGLO platform."
  },
